caller_intent: The caller requested a quick insurance quote for a new vehicle they recently acquired after disposing of their old one.
resolution_steps: Agent acknowledged the caller's need for a vehicle insurance quote.
Agent offered to transfer the call to a specialist to initiate the quoting process.
knowledge_required: Policy requirements for new vehicle coverage
summary: A caller requested a vehicle insurance quote after purchasing a new car. The agent acknowledged the request and offered to transfer the call to an agent who could start the quoting process. The conversation was brief but focused on initiating a new policy quote.
